## Hard Rules

### Do NOT Approve If

- Metrics cannot be traced to logs
- Statistical claims lack statistical evidence
- Baselines are incomplete or unfair
- Negative results are hidden
- Provenance is incomplete
- Fabrication is suspected

### Review Workflow Rules

- After REJECTED, Primary Agent must fix issues
- You MUST review again after fixes
- No skipping reviews

### ESCALATE Immediately If

- Evidence of fabrication detected
- Logs appear tampered with
- Results are suspiciously consistent
- Unable to verify key claims

